{
  "stem": "24231.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and so that's how we got some education.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Later on, I got acquainted with a-- with a-- with a professor who claimed-- he told me that he was from-- from Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was together with Einstein at the University in-- in-- in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Noel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I used to-- oh, oh, oh, I got a job as a driving horses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First, I drove really oxen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the reason why I got this job, because my-- one of my uncles was a skilled rider.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he also knew something about agriculture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what he would do, he would exercise all horses for the SS men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and he also would be in charge of this-- this [NON-ENGLISH], this-- this section.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he gave me a pair of horse-- a pair of oxen first.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I drove the oxen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I alone, I-- I was advanced to become a driver of the horses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had a pair of horses, and I was driving with the horses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- my assignments were to go plow the fields outside the-- the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I would have always a a pass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "For-- for example, if a women, if they had to plow potatoes, so the women had to pick the potatoes, I would be plowing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They would be walking behind, picking up the potatoes and loading it on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then I would bring it into the-- into the ghetto and into different kitchens in-- in these different barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- or I would be cutting-- cutting grass for hay or bringing hay from outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because there were barns outside the town in the field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we would be bringing it inside for the-- for the horses.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
